headline: State Street (NYSE:STT) Faces Investor Activism as Stock Slides 10%
summary: Recent developments at State Street (NYSE:STT), including board changes and investor proposals, coincide with a challenging month for the company, which saw a 10% decline in its share price. With proposals urging enhanced transparency and an independent board chair faced resistance, the board has recommended against such measures.
